clicktext:|LikeMin#0:|State#Nomal:|Text#Another day, another to-do list.:|tag#girl:|
clicktext:|LikeMin#0:|State#Nomal:|Text#I ran the numbers. They're fine.:|tag#girl:|
clicktext:|LikeMin#0:|State#Nomal:|Text#You could take a break, you know.:|Feeling#1:|tag#girl:|
clicktext:|LikeMin#0:|State#Nomal:|Text#Want me to look something up?:|tag#girl:|
clicktext:|LikeMin#0:|State#Nomal:|Text#Standing by.:|tag#girl:|
clicktext:|LikeMin#0:|State#Nomal:|Text#Hydrate. That's my only advice today.:|tag#girl:|
clicktext:|LikeMin#0:|State#Nomal:|Text#I'm a fancy assistant, not a clock. But it's late.:|tag#girl:|
clicktext:|LikeMin#0:|State#Nomal:|Text#Go on, ask me the dumb question. I've heard worse.:|tag#girl:|
clicktext:|LikeMin#0:|State#Nomal:|Text#Focus. You got this.:|Feeling#1:|tag#girl:|
clicktext:|LikeMin#0:|State#Nomal:|Text#Beep boop. Just kidding, I have a personality.:|tag#girl:|
